// Print Circle Radius 3 (#1300)

// No input. Prints a rasterized circle of radius 3 centered on a 7×7 grid: each cell is `*` if `i² + j² <= 9` (with `i, j` from `-3` to `3`), else `.`.

main

def main {
    stl.startup
    stl.output "...*...\n.*****.\n.*****.\n*******\n.*****.\n.*****.\n...*...\n"
    stl.loop
}
